      "body" : "My addition to this list is sqlite4java - <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/sqlite4java\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">code.google.com/p/sqlite4java</a> - it&#39;s a wrapper (no JDBC); precompiled for Windows, Mac, Linux. It&#39;s simple to use and it enforces some contracts to help the developer avoid misusing SQLite."
