    "question_id" : 41233,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The example code leads to a memory leak in Tomcat (after undeploying the webapp, the classloader still remains in memory) which will cause an <code>outofmemory</code> eventually. The way to solve it is to use the <a href=\"http://www.xerial.org/maven/repository/snapshot/org/xerial/sqlite-jdbc/3.7.8-SNAPSHOT/\" rel=\"nofollow\">sqlite-jdbc-3.7.8.jar</a>; it's a snapshot, so it doesn't appear for maven yet.</p>\n"
