      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Care to elaborate? On *nix the ; will seperate the java from the Test command (and therefore create a error). On Windows the : wont work as a cp seperator. So all in all <code>.:xxx.jar;</code> does not make sense. And you also need to specify the package name for the Test class."
