    "question_id" : 41233,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>sqlitejdbc code can be downloaded using git from <a href=\"https://github.com/crawshaw/sqlitejdbc\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/crawshaw/sqlitejdbc</a>. </p>\n\n<pre><code># git clone https://github.com/crawshaw/sqlitejdbc.git sqlitejdbc\n...\n# cd sqlitejdbc\n# make\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note: Makefile requires curl binary to download sqlite libraries/deps.</p>\n"
  } ],
